high_descs: Turn to the left and left again to find the microwave.
Pick up the spatula from the counter with the microwave.
Take the spatula and turn around to find the stove.
Place the spatula in the pan on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Carry the pan and turn around, then left and left again to face the white table.
Place the pan and spatula on the table, in the center.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and spatula to the table.

high_descs: Turn left and take two steps then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the stove.
Put the spatula in the pan that's on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it.
Take a step backwards then turn right and walk to the middle of the white table on your left turning left and walking to the table when you get there.
Put the pan to the left of the black cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Go to the table next to the fridge
Pick up a spatula from the table
Go to the stove
Place the spatula on a pan
Pick up the pan
Go to the white table
Place the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and spatula together to a table
